      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/china-banks-become-surprise-winners-of-frenzied-hunt-for-yield</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国经济陷入困境、房地产危机加剧之际，这可以说是股票投资者最不愿意转向的地方之一。]]></description>
