      <title>马来西亚债券有望成为新兴亚洲债券市场中涨幅最大的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/malaysian-bonds-set-to-gain-most-in-em-asia-from-treasury-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴亚洲债券对美国国债的敏感度正在回升至 2024 年的峰值，其中马来西亚债务将成为最大的受益者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/malaysian-bonds-set-to-gain-most-in-em-asia-from-treasury-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市迎来第三年创纪录退市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/chinese-stock-markets-head-for-third-year-of-record-delistings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于过去十年来首次公开募股 (IPO) 数量激增，以及为淘汰实力较弱的公司而出台的更严格规则，中国股市将连续第三年出现创纪录的退市数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/chinese-stock-markets-head-for-third-year-of-record-delistings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>绿色债务未能赶上印度债券市场的繁荣，低税率是印度的诱惑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/low-tax-is-india-s-lure-as-green-debt-misses-nation-s-bond-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于绿色债务错过了大量外国资金流入当地主权债券的机会，印度正在做出新的努力来激发人们对绿色债务的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/low-tax-is-india-s-lure-as-green-debt-misses-nation-s-bond-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
